name: Material Design Icons
description:
Instant easy access to the entire Material Design Icons library: 35,000+ icons in PNG and SVG at your fingertips. 

 

Search icons by name or scroll through the entire list. Filter by category, change style, size, and color. Available in all styles: outlined, filled, sharp, rounded, and two-tone.

 

What's inside

  • 6,800+ free icons by Google. You can find them in the "Google" section.
  • 28,000+ free icons by Icons8. We offer an extensive free tier. All we ask is to add a link back to Icons8.com, crediting us in the final work. If you don't want to add a link, consider buying a license. Additionally, you'll get access to all formats and sizes.

 

Original creator: Grappex.com
